c/pics/wandhama-victims.png","parent":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/index.html"},{"name":"./wandhama.js","dynamic":true,"resolved":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/wandhama.js","parent":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/index.html"},{"name":"/Users/u6075477/projects/.babelrc","includedInParent":true,"mtime":1556862282399},{"name":"/Users/u6075477/projects/wandhama/package.json","includedInParent":true,"mtime":1610182172116}],"generated":{"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><title>Document</title><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\"><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=PT+Serif&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@splidejs/splide@latest/dist/js/splide.min.js\"></script><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@splidejs/splide@latest/dist/css/splide.min.css\"><link href=\"/wandhama/cbe08353cc4beeaa4203d86039afc03c.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"></head><body> <div class=\"splide\"> <div class=\"splide__arrows\"> <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--prev\"> <i class=\"icon-up-open\"></i> </button> <button class=\"splide__arrow splide__arrow--next\"> <i class=\"icon-down-open\"></i> </button> </div> <div class=\"splide__track\"> <ul class=\"splide__list\"> <li class=\"top splide__slide slide\"> <h1 class=\"headline\">A nightmare revisited</h1> <p class=\"subhed\">Reliving the Wandhama massacre of 1998. </p>  </li> <li class=\"text-map splide__slide slide text-slide\"> <p> Wandhama is a quiet village in central Kashmir’s Ganderbal district. The name in Kashmiri means ‘hot in winter’ i.e. providing comfort to its people. </p> <div class=\"wandhama-locator\"> <img src=\"/wandhama/695c592ffd5f6c0964cb62ae269d397a.png\"> <img class=\"overlay-dot\" src=\"/wandhama/9a112a59a6dc34be62f15f660c0ac194.png\">  </div> </li> <li class=\"text-failed splide__slide slide text-slide\"> <p> But on 25th January 1998, Wandhama failed to live upto it's name. It witnessed the killing of 23 Kashmiri Hindus in the dead of the night by unidentified gunmen. </p> <div class=\"slide-pics\"> <img class=\"no-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/ec14ea5820b0a41a4fd26a880cecab5c.jpg\"> <img class=\"hover-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/9cf0f9bedaa0aa25bc945511955427da.png\">  </div> </li>  <li class=\"text-solo splide__slide slide text-slide\"> <p> The events of that night are recalled by one of the survivors of the incident, a 14-year-old Hindu boy named Vinod Kuman Dhar alias Ashu. The teenager had slipped away and hidden himself in a dark corner of the house. </p> </li> <li class=\"text-house splide__slide slide text-slide\"> <p class=\"darker\"> “The gunmen were dressed like Indian Army soldiers,”, Ashu said piecing the details together. “They had tea with us, waiting for a radio message indicating that all pandit families in the village had been covered.” </p> <div class=\"wandhama-house slide-pics\"> <img class=\"no-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/3f536d14e4c4ea8f0c46ace46f0255ee.png\"> <img class=\"hover-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/e3afd09a89edb7626b46e38b84c70544.png\"> </div> </li> <li class=\"text-bodies splide__slide slide text-slide\"> <p> After a brief conversation they rounded up all the members of the Hindu households and then gunned them down with Kalashnikov rifles. </p> <div class=\"wandhama-bodies slide-pics\"> <img class=\"no-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/d0aa8cc395c042d0eff543a81a4b3e10.jpg\"> <img class=\"hover-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/bcc1ea7052b5e7d8cbee0ad81c1f31f4.jpg\"> </div> </li> <li class=\"text-burning splide__slide slide text-slide\"> <p> There was burning smell of the human flesh everywhere. A mother had unsuccessfully tried to save her infant by hiding him in her lap but both got killed together. The cop trying to separate them couldn’t. </p> <div class=\"slide-pics\"> <img class=\"no-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/2ab9e2ec78760160b2d5de884829c374.png\"> <img class=\"hover-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/2ab9e2ec78760160b2d5de884829c374.png\"> </div> </li> <li class=\"text-victims splide__slide slide text-slide\"> <p class=\"darker\"> The neighbourhood had changed forever. The victims included 10 men, 9 women and 4 children. <span style=\"margin-top:20px;display:block;\">These are their stories.</span> </p> <div class=\"slide-pics\"> <img class=\"no-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/34b4fd5b32a5d0ee20b98218ba8ccd6f.png\"> <img class=\"hover-highlight\" src=\"/wandhama/34b4fd5b32a5d0ee20b98218ba8ccd6f.png\"> </div> </li> <li class=\"photos splide__slide slide\"> <div class=\"photo-row row-1\"> <p class=\"family-name\">X Family</p> </div> <div class=\"photo-row row-2\"> <p class=\"family-name\">Y Family</p> </div> <div class=\"photo-row row-3\"> <p class=\"family-name\">Z family</p> </div> <div class=\"photo-row row-4\"> <p class=\"family-name\">W family</p> </div> <div class=\"pic-description\"> <p class=\"name\"></p> <p class=\"age\"></p> </div> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </body><script src=\"/wandhama/ca536e47f3f828a66947fddf7b1dc418.js\"></script></html>"},"sourceMaps":null,"error":null,"hash":"261df90e909ee66cc53908514ed4155c","cacheData":{"env":{}}}